  "_doc": "Mental Health at Work Pledge signatories — a coalition program launched in 2022 by Mind Share Partners with the Society for Human Resource Management (SHRM), One Mind at Work, and others. Signatories commit to (1) building a strategic plan for workplace mental health, (2) C-suite accountability, and (3) measuring outcomes. ALSO includes the One Mind at Work CEO Pledge and the American Psychiatric Association Foundation Center for Workplace Mental Health 'Notable Practices' list — together the canonical public US workplace-mental-health commitment set. Fills the brief's explicit 'workplace mental health' gap. Sources: https://www.mindsharepartners.org/mental-health-at-work-pledge + https://onemind.org/onemindatwork/",
